Zootopia may appear to be this happy, go lucky city but what if I told you that it is actually DOOMED to fail. I know it may seem like a utopia of just innocent Disney animals but what if a place like this actually existed, scientifically? Would it even stand a chance to survive? The true answer may shock you…
